&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role...&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As the Director of Product Management for the new Short-form Learning Area, you&#39;ll own the core of Duolingo: the bite-sized, gamified lessons that instruct learners in a fun and effective way. You will manage a team of senior product managers to improve our existing exercises, develop new ones, and use AI to teach as effectively as possible.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In addition to your product leadership responsibilities, as Area Lead, you&#39;ll partner with your engineering and learning co-leads to lead a group of 75 cross-functional colleagues across engineering, product, design, and learning and curriculum. Together, you will make sure learning a language on Duolingo is effective and delightful. You&#39;ll also partner with other product leaders across the company to ensure we&#39;re delivering a cohesive experience across learning formats.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Some of the problems you will own include...&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Making every bite-sized exercise effective and delightful&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Teaching grammar more effectively&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Improving our Chinese, Japanese, and Korean courses&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Using AI to customize the learning path&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
