&lt;li&gt;Manage and develop a team of senior product managers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Level up your team&#39;s product craft and velocity, so we&#39;re producing higher-quality work, faster&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead through example by using AI to improve your craft, and encouraging your team to do the same&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Propose and own key initiatives that improve the entire product org (e.g., AI adoption, interviewing, performance management)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
